00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:12.000
Another big caveat is, like, this is all fun if you're just trying to do some analysis.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:17.000
Like, hey, I really want this data from this baseball game or from this government website or whatever.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:20.000
Do not build a business around, like, the tools.

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:25.000
Because eventually if you're hitting this thing, like, if you hit it once every now and then, no one's ever going to notice.

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.000
They're just going to think you're a web browser.

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:35.000
If you're, like, banging some private API, just pounding away at it, like, with, like, a, you know, cron job every minute.

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:38.000
Like, they're eventually going to figure that out and probably block your IP address.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:39.000
So, like, don't do that.

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:43.000
Don't build out, like, some big, don't think, ah-ha, now I have a great business idea.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:45.000
I'm going to create this weird API and do this.

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:47.000
Don't do that.

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:49.000
